cloudy; Knoxville 31 foggy; Macon 38 foggy; Miami 55 partly cloudy;
New York 32 cloudy; Philadelphia 23 fair; Pittsburgh 26 foggy;
Portland, Maine, 17 fair; Richmond 33 foggy; Tampa 42 fair;
Washington, D.C. 26 foggy.
